            <h2>Conclusion</h2>
            <p>NVIDIA NIM occupies a unique position in the AI API market. It is not trying to beat Groq on speed, Together AI on model breadth, or Novita AI on China access. Instead, it is a gateway into the NVIDIA ecosystem — a way to try NVIDIA's exclusive Nemotron-3 models before committing to self-hosted NIM containers on your own GPU infrastructure.</p>
            <p>The decision tree for picking a provider in 2026:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Need NVIDIA's exclusive Nemotron-3 architecture for evaluation → <strong>NVIDIA NIM (free tier)</strong></li>
              <li>Need the Nemotron-3 Ultra 550B at the cheapest rate → <strong>NVIDIA NIM via Deep Infra</strong></li>
