              <li>Need the fastest inference speed on a specific model → <strong>Groq or Cerebras</strong></li>
            </ul>
            <p>If your team is experimenting with NVIDIA's Nemotron models and wants a production fallback for multi-provider routing from China, FreeModel complements the setup — it bundles moderation routing, OpenAI/Anthropic access, and direct China connectivity behind one API key. Sign up at <a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220</a>.</p>

